277
00:24:30,200 --> 00:24:32,240
You will find a satisfactory husband.

278
00:24:32,240 --> 00:24:34,600
Though the world is big, Cousin can’t be copied.

279
00:24:34,720 --> 00:24:36,600
I only love Cousin.

280
00:24:38,520 --> 00:24:40,560
No, I need to meet Cousin.

281
00:24:41,080 --> 00:24:41,840
Stop!

282
00:24:44,280 --> 00:24:45,120
Qi Chong!

283
00:24:47,240 --> 00:24:47,840
Your Excellency Duke.

284
00:24:48,240 --> 00:24:49,760
Send princess back to her room.

285
