287
00:24:55,040 --> 00:24:55,800
Yes!

288
00:24:56,280 --> 00:24:58,480
Princess, please.

289
00:24:59,240 --> 00:25:00,880
Even if you bring my cousin down from the throne,

290
00:25:00,880 --> 00:25:04,000
I will only marry him in my life.

291
00:25:07,640 --> 00:25:10,040
Here comes His Majesty!

292
00:25:26,280 --> 00:25:28,960
May you healthy, Your Majesty!

293
00:25:30,720 --> 00:25:31,360
Stand up.

294
00:25:31,800 --> 00:25:33,480
Thank you, Your Majesty!

295
00:25:36,560 --> 00:25:40,040
What is the important thing today?

296
00:25:42,520 --> 00:25:44,000
Your Majesty,

297
00:25:44,440 --> 00:25:46,920
I originally couldn’t bear to

298
00:25:46,920 --> 00:25:48,040
