300
00:25:52,400 --> 00:25:54,840
It really can’t be delayed.

301
00:25:55,720 --> 00:25:56,880
What is so important?

302
00:25:57,590 --> 00:25:58,380
Tell me.

303
00:26:04,360 --> 00:26:07,320
Your Majesty is ill and doesn’t have any child.

304
00:26:07,800 --> 00:26:09,760
In addition, it is a period of trouble.

305
00:26:09,760 --> 00:26:11,920
So we believe

306
00:26:12,440 --> 00:26:14,720
Your Majesty should put the state and people first

307
00:26:14,720 --> 00:26:16,150
and abdicate to a virtuous man.

308
00:26:16,630 --> 00:26:18,360
In this case,
we won’t fail the spirit of the ancestors.

309
00:26:24,040 --> 00:26:28,800
You think I am ill
and can’t shoulder the important task.

310
00:26:29,560 --> 00:26:30,620
The previous king died early.

311
00:26:31,040 --> 00:26:32,870
Your Majesty acceded to the throne
at a very young age.

312
00:26:33,440 --> 00:26:36,170
With a young king, the state was doubted,
with internal and external problems.

313
00:26:36,720 --> 00:26:39,550
Fortunately, Duke Nanping
made vigorous efforts to turn the situation,

314
00:26:39,880 --> 00:26:40,840
delivering the state from distress.

315
00:26:41,080 --> 00:26:42,170
The former example is before our eyes.

316
00:26:42,630 --> 00:26:44,800
Hope Your Majesty
can set store by overall interests.

317
00:26:45,120 --> 00:26:46,890
Following the example of Yao and Shun’s abdication

318
00:26:47,100 --> 00:26:48,140
has long been set in the fundamental principles.

319
00:26:48,160 --> 00:26:52,280
According to you, if I don’t abdicate,

320
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:56,080
I will be a sinner of Huaiwu.

321
00:26:57,240 --> 00:26:58,760
I dare not.

322
00:26:58,760 --> 00:27:00,000
Then tell me.

323
00:27:00,280 --> 00:27:03,840
If I abdicate, who can take over the throne?

324
00:27:04,760 --> 00:27:07,840
We must recommend an upright wise king

325
00:27:07,840 --> 00:27:09,480
who possesses both integrity and ability.

326
00:27:09,880 --> 00:27:13,000
An upright wise king with integrity and ability?

327
00:27:15,960 --> 00:27:20,600
I wonder if Duke Nanping
wants to form alliances with various dukes

328
00:27:21,320 --> 00:27:24,040
or Minister Fu wants to unite the country.

329
00:27:25,040 --> 00:27:27,640
Your Majesty, I deserve death.

330
00:27:27,800 --> 00:27:30,280
If I have the intention to rebel,
I would stand condemned by God.

331
00:27:30,520 --> 00:27:33,160
Your Majesty, I dare not.

332
00:27:33,800 --> 00:27:36,520
Liu Si said so much to ask you to abdicate,
so he is guilty.

333
00:27:36,520 --> 00:27:38,320
Please punish him, Your Majesty.

334
00:27:39,160 --> 00:27:42,280
Your Majesty, my royalty
could be discerned by the sun and moon.

335
00:27:43,160 --> 00:27:43,840
Mr. Liu,

336
00:27:45,280 --> 00:27:48,680
you said I am seriously ill

337
00:27:48,920 --> 00:27:50,240
and will die soon.

338
00:27:50,720 --> 00:27:52,800
Where did you

339
00:27:52,800 --> 00:27:53,920
get the news?

340
00:27:54,480 --> 00:27:57,520
Recently, Saint Girl of Saint Doctors’ Family
went to the palace to treat your illness.

341
00:27:58,160 --> 00:28:00,520
We’ll know by asking her.

342
00:28:02,360 --> 00:28:05,080
OK. Summon Saint Girl.

343
00:28:06,000 --> 00:28:08,120
Summon Jin Mi, Saint Girl of Saint Doctors’ Family.

344
00:28:26,560 --> 00:28:29,680
Jin Mi, Saint Girl of Saint Doctors’ Family
pays a visit to Your Majesty.

345
00:28:31,720 --> 00:28:32,360
Forego the formalities.

346
00:28:32,840 --> 00:28:33,920
Thanks, Your Majesty.

347
00:28:34,960 --> 00:28:36,000
Tell me

348
00:28:36,320 --> 00:28:39,440
what illness I have got.

349
00:28:49,160 --> 00:28:52,720
Previously, Your Majesty
got up before dawn, ate late and overworked,

350
00:28:53,200 --> 00:28:55,560
so he was indeed a little weak.

351
00:29:01,880 --> 00:29:02,840
But,

352
00:29:04,840 --> 00:29:06,240
after being nursed by me,

353
00:29:06,640 --> 00:29:09,920
Your Majesty is strong and has recovered.

354
00:29:39,280 --> 00:29:42,000
Your Majesty, I’ve received news
from the men sent to Saint Doctors’ Family.

355
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:42,680
How is it?

356
00:29:43,360 --> 00:29:44,560
Everyone of Saint Doctors’ Family is safe.

357
00:29:45,160 --> 00:29:46,120
Our men

358
00:29:46,400 --> 00:29:48,240
are protecting them well.

359
00:29:48,240 --> 00:29:50,920
Duke Nanping’s men all died.

360
00:29:51,760 --> 00:29:54,120
Duke Nanping is always careful and heartless.

361
00:29:55,040 --> 00:29:57,480
Arrange more men to project Saint Girl.

362
00:29:57,480 --> 00:29:58,760
Do not let Duke Nanping

363
00:29:58,760 --> 00:30:00,440
get close to her.

364
00:30:00,440 --> 00:30:00,960
Yes.

365
00:30:04,560 --> 00:30:05,960
Previously, you said

366
00:30:06,120 --> 00:30:09,080
Your Majesty’s kidney yang and blood are weak,
so his six yang have problems.

367
00:30:09,520 --> 00:30:10,560
As for this,

368
00:30:10,920 --> 00:30:14,080
I was indeed inexperienced before,

369
00:30:14,240 --> 00:30:16,200
so I made some erroneous judgment.

370
00:30:16,760 --> 00:30:20,960
But these diagnoses are extremely private.

371
00:30:20,960 --> 00:30:23,240
I remember I have never told Your Excellency these.

372
00:30:23,240 --> 00:30:26,360
I wonder where Your Excellency got the news.

373
00:30:26,840 --> 00:30:30,240
As Saint Girl, how could you make such an error?

374
00:30:30,480 --> 00:30:33,040
How dare you treat Your Majesty slightly?

375
00:30:33,040 --> 00:30:34,240
Your Excellency Duke, please don’t be angry.

376
00:30:35,880 --> 00:30:39,120
Your Majesty, I made such an error

377
00:30:39,280 --> 00:30:40,600
because

378
00:30:41,360 --> 00:30:45,120
someone tampered with Your Majesty’s diets.

379
00:30:51,800 --> 00:30:54,760
The diets on the diet list seem nourish,

380
00:30:55,320 --> 00:30:56,720
but their properties go against each other.

381
00:30:57,400 --> 00:30:59,640
Most of them are strong drugs of
eighteen incompatibilities and nineteen counteractions.

382
00:31:00,360 --> 00:31:01,920
If Your Majesty takes them for a long time,

383
00:31:01,920 --> 00:31:03,800
the consequence will be unthinkable.

384
00:31:05,280 --> 00:31:08,160
Where is the diet list from?

385
00:31:08,520 --> 00:31:09,640
The diet list…

386
00:31:12,040 --> 00:31:13,080
Your Majesty,

387
00:31:13,480 --> 00:31:16,320
Saint Girl asked me
about the diet list some days ago.

388
00:31:16,840 --> 00:31:20,190
I asked Dong Ruixi, Manager of Food Supervisor,

389
00:31:20,610 --> 00:31:21,650
to copy one.

390
00:31:21,800 --> 00:31:23,160
Now it seems

391
00:31:24,440 --> 00:31:26,760
Dong Ruixi is very suspicious.

392
00:31:33,480 --> 00:31:34,960
Summon Dong Ruixi.

393
00:31:41,960 --> 00:31:47,200
Dong Ruixi, is the diet list made by you?

394
00:31:48,720 --> 00:31:52,960
Your Majesty, it is made by me.

395
00:31:54,160 --> 00:31:56,400
Do you know the tonic diets on it

396
00:31:56,600 --> 00:31:58,400
