397
00:31:59,160 --> 00:32:02,720
Who is behind this?

398
00:32:04,640 --> 00:32:08,640
Tell me your accomplice, and I will spare you.

399
00:32:12,280 --> 00:32:12,960
Your Majesty,

400
00:32:14,280 --> 00:32:15,720
I don’t have accomplice

401
00:32:17,120 --> 00:32:18,720
and I have never acted on anyone’s instigation.

402
00:32:20,480 --> 00:32:23,000
Your Majesty, this man is vicious

403
00:32:23,000 --> 00:32:24,720
