404
00:32:24,720 --> 00:32:28,440
He must been beheaded as a warning to others.

405
00:32:29,960 --> 00:32:32,920
Your Majesty, this matter has many doubtful points.

406
00:32:33,320 --> 00:32:37,280
I suggest putting Dong Ruixi into prison
and investigating this matter.

407
00:32:37,600 --> 00:32:38,440
Put him into prison.

408
00:32:39,920 --> 00:32:40,600
Go.

409
00:32:41,240 --> 00:32:41,840
Go.

410
00:32:48,440 --> 00:32:49,320
Minister Fu.

411
00:32:50,320 --> 00:32:51,000
Here I am.

412
00:32:51,080 --> 00:32:53,400
You’ll be responsible for this.

413
00:32:54,080 --> 00:32:55,800
Yes, Your Majesty.

414
00:33:03,320 --> 00:33:03,960
Officials.

415
00:33:04,760 --> 00:33:07,160
When people have many “weapons,”
the sate will be in chaos.

416
00:33:08,080 --> 00:33:10,560
When people have more skills,
strange things will appear.

417
00:33:12,520 --> 00:33:15,960
Hope you can fulfill their duties

418
00:33:16,560 --> 00:33:17,680
and learn from Duke Nanping

419
00:33:17,680 --> 00:33:20,240
who is upright with both ability and integrity.

420
00:33:21,400 --> 00:33:24,640
Having such an upright minister,
I am rather content.

421
00:33:24,640 --> 00:33:28,160
Thanks for your praise, Your Majesty.

422
00:33:29,040 --> 00:33:31,960
We will follow Your Majesty’s order.

423
00:33:42,120 --> 00:33:42,840
Your Excellency Duke,

424
00:33:42,840 --> 00:33:44,680
