425
00:34:14,440 --> 00:34:15,190
Remember.

426
00:34:15,690 --> 00:34:17,690
Do not let Dong Ruixi speak again.

427
00:34:19,320 --> 00:34:20,239
I see.

428
00:34:39,960 --> 00:34:40,639
Buddha,

429
00:34:41,239 --> 00:34:42,679
please bless my cousin

430
00:34:42,679 --> 00:34:44,280
